EN: This is a professional-grade scale that can weigh all kinds of items.

ZH: 我需要一个新的厨房秤来称量食材。
EN: I need a new kitchen scale to weigh ingredients.

ZH: 这个秤是不准确的，必须要调整一下。
EN: This scale is inaccurate and needs to be adjusted.

ZH: 请你拿一把秤来称重土豆。
